OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright day with some low
OL,6,Fcloud lingering along the Kent coast
OL,7,Fin the morning. A fresh northeasterly
OL,8,Fwind by the sea. Feeling hot inland,
OL,9,Fcooler along coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FLow cloud over the North Sea
OL,12,Fwill spread inland in the east of the
OL,13,Fregion by the morning. The
OL,14,Fnortheasterly breeze becomes very
OL,15,Fbreezy along the coast. Temperatures
OL,16,Fremain mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
