OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloudy periods to start
OL,6,FSunday, the low cloud will clear
OL,7,Fgiving hazy sunshine during the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Temperatures very warm,
OL,9,Flocally hot, but cooler along the
OL,10,Fcoast in the northeasterly breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,13,Fand largely sunny conditions on Monday
OL,14,Fwith coastal cloud. Some patchy cloud
OL,15,FTuesday morning, brightening up later.
OL,16,FA cloudy start to Wednesday with
OL,17,Fafternoon showers. Temperatures around
OL,18,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
